{"tid":1568301,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[平民廚房][圖文片][請人] 羊肉Burger & 薄荷乳酪醬","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T19:37:13.000Z","uid":156466,"like":122,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"71f70ee4b0a9fbcb501b0c52bcdae6f4f1278299","tid":1568301,"uid":156466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"好記得有位紅字user留cm留左幾年話想睇羊肉burger <br />\n終於，拍左衣條整羊肉Burger既片!!<br />\n今次我揀左衣個薄荷乳酪汁去襯個Burger，帶印度風味，希望大家有興趣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而衣個Post既另一目的就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想請熱血既戰士黎我廚房返工<br />\n白紙定係有經驗人仕都歡迎，樓面都歡迎見工<br />\n可以隨時tg我呀，多謝!</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TG: SeafoodPeter</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n衣條片其實真係拍左好耐好耐，但當我edit完準備好出片時，香港就病了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n希望各位都可以堅持落去，為左香港而付出既同時亦不忙照顧自己，亦唔好介意受人幫助。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n我好希望，今時今日見證到既香港人既美好，係未來都可以保持住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去片!<br />\nYoutube Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uf-a4CAml2Q&amp;t=29s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duf-a4CAml2Q%26t%3D29s&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a25c0047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uf-a4CAml2Q&amp;t=29s</a><br />\n<br />\n圖文開波!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jW3vZud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjW3vZud.jpg&h=4a2e925d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1. 切哂整羊burger肉D材料先，材料切碎至跟羊肉免治size差唔多就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSk6xPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSk6xPs.jpg&h=a33e697f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2. 倒哂D料落去，撈勻哂先。<br />\n之後就用力壓下佢，搓下佢。<br />\n壓佢衣個動作就可以將D羊色治盡量捽散佢，等成兜野撈到勻巡D。<br />\n然後我地可以撻下D肉，撻到佢有少少黏性就OK了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2FycQm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2FycQm.jpg&h=95ade81f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm9ZSQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm9ZSQn.jpg&h=148b78d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmSHQB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmSHQB2.jpg&h=31198a85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3. 整Mint yougurt醬，第一步係切開D材料先，唔洗切太碎。<br />\n切青辣椒前，我地可以壓一壓、碌一碌條辣椒，再係中間劏開佢一半，挖哂D椒籽出黎。<br />\n放哂D材料入Blender (記得加水，如果唔係就會好似Ivan咁打唔郁D野)，<br />\n水份要著量，唔好一次過加太多，最後出黎太稀或太稠都唔好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCei8o1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCei8o1.jpg&h=894ba2e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4. 打到佢差唔多變哂做綠色汁汁，就可以加埋D Plain yogurt落去，<br />\n加yogurt除左要佢個味，亦可以令到成個醬個質感更加滑。<br />\n記得要試試味先，可以俾返個味去，落返D鹽、糖，試味試到岩為止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGRNhhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGRNhhG.jpg&h=d540816e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n5. 係搓burger前，可以拎一細粒肉仔煎黎食下佢個味岩唔岩心水。<br />\n如果唔岩心水，太鹹就可以加返多D肉、糖、薄荷葉落去中和返個味度。<br />\n咁唔夠鹹既話就當然係著量再落返多些少鹽啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSTXhV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSTXhV.jpg&h=d36d71f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akpK3XV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakpK3XV.jpg&h=a5728031&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n6. 搓burger，係我地餐廳既話就會搓一個大約200g既burger肉出黎。<br />\n咁係屋企自己整既話就你喜歡啦。<br />\n拎左D肉上手之後，係兩手之間來回撻下佢。<br />\n搓左出黎之後，記得要係中間位用手指壓一壓凹佢。<br />\n作用係等陣間煎肉時佢唔會成個脹到好似波咁，頂住個burger bun。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAt4jwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAt4jwE.jpg&h=cd3f4c50&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxp7hij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxp7hij.jpg&h=8d45d67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7. 可以正式煎肉喇。<br />\n熱鑊落油，放舊肉上去。煎到兩面都有色，就可以拎個焗盤出黎，放肉上去，入焗爐。<br />\n大約3-4分鐘左右就可以拎出黎試下佢熟未。<br />\n搵枝銀針出黎，吉入去肉心，然後試試銀針個個位夠唔夠熱，唔會辣親你而又夠熱既話就OK! (叫做高暖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuPfrbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuPfrbR.jpg&h=c65ebe99&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxiDoYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxiDoYx.jpg&h=7405285a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n8. 烘一烘個burger bun俾D色水佢先。<br />\n烘完之後就可以放芝士上burger bun同burger肉上面，再拎去焗，焗到D芝士溶溶地就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1k6Jz5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1k6Jz5x.jpg&h=bfd6bc81&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyGYoYT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyGYoYT.jpg&h=95d72ab4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkfN1Lz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkfN1Lz.jpg&h=46f5411b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n9. 係時候組裝成個burger喇。<br />\n係底層包上面放上生菜、紫洋蔥等配菜，放埋舊肉上去，淋上Mint yogurt，<br />\n擺埋面層個個包上去。由於成個包已經疊到好高，我地可以換竹籤插住個包去固定佢。<br />\n除你個人喜好，咁我地餐廳出菜俾客人就緊係會有埋薯條同沙律啦。<br />\n去到衣步就大功告成，食得!<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望request我既個位紅字user會睇到啦!"},{"pid":"bb8c8e1167753231cc78a8b75af004b9327fb4b0","tid":1568301,"uid":1590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"First TUI<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55923620f9d8c5a329960309bb9666a3b9f5f55b","tid":1568301,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"良心老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a5915c